FBIS4-12994 "drnes073_l_94013" FBIS-NES-94-073 Daily Report 13 Apr 1994 ISRAEL Poll: Majority Disapprove of Government Performance Poll: Majority Disapprove of Government Performance TA1304173894 Tel Aviv YEDI'OT AHARONOT in Hebrew 13 Apr 94 p 1 TA1304173894 Tel Aviv YEDI'OT AHARONOT Hebrew BFN [Public opinion poll conducted by the Dahaf Institute under the management of Dr. Mina Tzemah] [Excerpt] [passage omitted] How do you rate the Israeli Government's performance? ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Good |41 percent. | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |Not good |58 percent. | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |No reply |1 percent. | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------- The poll was conducted on 10 and 11 April, questioning 504 interviewees who constitute a representative sample of Israel's adult population. Maximal margin of error is four percent.
